                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="1to4">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">** Slotted Nut and Cotter Pin Assembly Procedure</emph>
                            </para>
                            <seqlist style="ARABIC">
                                <item>
                                    <para>Tighten the nut to initial torque specified.</para>
                                </item>
                                <item>
                                    <para>Advance the nut (Do not back it off) to align the cotter pin.</para>
                                </item>
                                <item>
                                    <para>Final installed torque Must Not exceed the maximum specified.</para>
                                </item>
                                <item>
                                    <para>If final torque exceeds the maximum, remove the nut and reinstall to correct
                                        specification.
                                    </para>
                                </item>
                            </seqlist>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="1to4">
                            <important>
                                <para>*** The correct torque must be reached on steering arms. Torques below minimum
                                    will not seat the tapers properly and reduce service life.
                                </para>
                            </important>
